Cloudwatch logs for EC2

By defaul no logs from your ec2 machine will go int cloudwatch
you need to run a cloudwatch agent on ec2 to push the log files you want
make sure IAM permissions are correct
the cloudwatch log agent can be setup on premises

-------------------

Logs agent and unified agent

For virtual servers
Cloudwatch logs agent:
  old version
  only to cloudwatch
unified agent
  collect addiotional system level metrics
  collect logs to send to cloudwatch logs
  centralized configuration using SSM parameter store

---------------------------

Metrics

Collect directly on your linux server/ec2 instance

CPU
Disk Metrics
RAM
NetStats
Processes
Swap Space

Notes: out of the box metrics for ec2
